        <section classes="classref-descriptions-group" ids="id6" names="方法说明">
            <title>方法说明</title>
            <target refid="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-get-contact-body"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-get-contact-body" names="class_vehiclewheel3d_method_get_contact_body"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_node3d#class-node3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">Node3D</inline></reference> <strong>get_contact_body</strong> <strong>(</strong> <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>如果接触的实体节点在树中有效，则返回接触的实体节点，如 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_node3d#class-node3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">Node3D</inline></reference>。目前，不支持 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_gridmap#class-gridmap"><inline classes="std std-ref">GridMap</inline></reference>，因此该节点将始终为 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_physicsbody3d#class-physicsbody3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">PhysicsBody3D</inline></reference> 类型。</paragraph>
            <paragraph>如果车轮没有与表面接触，或者接触的实体不是 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_physicsbody3d#class-physicsbody3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">PhysicsBody3D</inline></reference>，则返回 <literal>null</literal>。</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-get-rpm"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-get-rpm" names="class_vehiclewheel3d_method_get_rpm"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_float#class-float"><inline classes="std std-ref">float</inline></reference> <strong>get_rpm</strong> <strong>(</strong> <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>返回轮子的旋转速度，单位为每分钟转数。</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-get-skidinfo"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-get-skidinfo" names="class_vehiclewheel3d_method_get_skidinfo"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_float#class-float"><inline classes="std std-ref">float</inline></reference> <strong>get_skidinfo</strong> <strong>(</strong> <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>返回一个介于 0.0 和 1.0 之间的值，表示这个轮子是否打滑。0.0 表示打滑（车轮失去了抓地力，例如冰雪地形），1.0 表示不打滑（车轮有充分的抓地力，例如干燥的沥青路）。</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-is-in-contact"></target>
            <paragraph classes="classref-method" ids="class-vehiclewheel3d-method-is-in-contact" names="class_vehiclewheel3d_method_is_in_contact"><reference internal="True" refuri="class_bool#class-bool"><inline classes="std std-ref">bool</inline></reference> <strong>is_in_contact</strong> <strong>(</strong> <strong>)</strong> <abbreviation explanation="本方法没有副作用。不会修改该实例的任何成员变量。">const</abbreviation></paragraph>
            <paragraph>如果轮子与表面接触，返回 <literal>true</literal>。</paragraph>
